{"tid":993840,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"人間芭比！　Lisa露Bra性感破尺度","createTime":"2019-01-24T08:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T14:33:27.000Z","uid":74065,"like":6,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1c46c44ba9dfeb8f3b680db6005cf23ffd31f0ba","tid":993840,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:30:51.000Z","msg":"南韓人氣女團BLACKPINK泰國籍成員Lisa有著洋娃娃般外貌，個性活潑大方加上舞蹈實力堅強，圈粉無數。日前超越少女時代隊長太妍，成為Instagram追蹤人數最多的南韓女星，去年她也成為除了子瑜之外，入選「全球最美臉孔」前10名的南韓偶像歌手，近日她獨自登上時尚雜誌封面，挑戰甜美之外的性感風格。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3858/d3858168.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3858%2Fd3858168.jpg&h=b79d9dc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Lisa 2018年入選「全球最美臉孔」第9名。（圖／翻攝自Youtube／TC Candler）<br />\n<br />\nLisa日前首次在沒有BLACKPINK成員陪伴下，獨自登上韓國版《DAZED KOREA》封面，過去大多走甜美搖滾風，這次拍攝的4組照片則嘗試不同衣著風格，金色平肩亮片短洋裝更讓她像個洋娃娃，到了皮革連身工作服，她上半身拉鍊全開，露出內搭的黑色Bra，看起來相當性感，臉上接近素顏的妝容也讓她不失清純感。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3858/d3858165.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3858%2Fd3858165.jpg&h=2c988811&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼Lisa登上時尚雜誌封面。（圖／翻攝自《DAZED KOREA》IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3858/d3858164.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3858%2Fd3858164.jpg&h=e032888f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLisa雖然2018年6月中才開設Instagram帳號，但成立僅7個月時間，就吸引超過1390萬人追蹤，成長速度相當驚人，也逆轉太妍的1300萬追蹤數，成為Follow人數最多的南韓女星。"},{"pid":"d2a05c308b05ca77aed617e8f359215d0ea7450b","tid":993840,"uid":74065,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:34:58.000Z","msg":"意為係LISA汪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8911e67a1bdf49afdb4614795fa9b81647cfd74","tid":993840,"uid":76753,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:36:39.000Z","msg":"入黎想睇阿姐<img src=\"/a